{"about_the_game":"<strong>For those of you who are unable to see their loved ones ever again</strong>.<br><br>I can't see them anymore. But I really wish that I could see and hold them again. Where is my special person? I wonder if I will ever meet them again. &quot;In His Time&quot; is a 2D mystery-solving adventure game that faces these feelings.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/gif_0.gif?t=1734938040\" /><br><br>The main character Olly, a young boy who lost his father early, lives with his mother Lyla. His mother has recently become ill, so he is left to attend school and take care of the housework.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/gif_2_en.gif?t=1734938040\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/gif_3.gif?t=1734938040\" /><br><br>Even at school, Olly is bullied by Bobby the big kid, and his cronies Mila and Hugo. He is also scolded by his teachers every day....... It was as if the world was pushing Ollie into a corner.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/gif_1_en.gif?t=1734938040\" /><br><br>One day Olly is threatened by Bobby and his friends and together they sneak into a spooky mansion. They steal &quot;parts&quot; of a certain work and escape, only to be caught by the owner of the house - an old man named Joseph. Joseph, who claims to be a watchmaker, asks Olly what happened to him and says he won't do anything bad to Olly if he gets the &quot;parts&quot; back from Bobby and his friends.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/gif_4_en.gif?t=1734938040\" /><br><br>Will Olly be able to reconcile with Bobby and the others? What will happen to his mother? And who is Joseph? Olly's adventure begins. We hope you will join us to see how it ends and how he develops!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/gif_5.gif?t=1734938040\" /><br><br><strong>Introduction of Characters</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/In_His_Time_chara_AD_EN_620_349_0629_OPsample0703.jpg?t=1734938040\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unpleasant Dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/59b6ffcfab1ea731dc4927809e7806a9388734f4.jpg"},{"name":"Very Bad Boy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/d45f2c3529245ea8c6bf0b023a4e586a3fb5e962.jpg"},{"name":"Wanted Person","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/654fed9ccf0ca3265d6fa0b1a7dd59cd3f83837a.jpg"},{"name":"What was Mine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/f401e192b3898030dcd9a44789142c0538809fe0.jpg"},{"name":"Here We Are","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/988893e0c9dc63a1763971d91112a623443ee26c.jpg"},{"name":"Wonderful Awakening","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/c6aebe7f71b4b6d485161a0ec5e006a3190c6cda.jpg"},{"name":"Something to Show","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/50f40afdf1369c48eac280a3e67ef361d19f9a16.jpg"},{"name":"No More Cheating","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/120966c333e821976ee42ff0b86549fecf057a7c.jpg"},{"name":"Starting Over Today...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2361610/e9020c07430342509bf0fecd1daf2d94b08859d5.jpg"},{"name":"To Be Forgiven","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunit